  "descriptionParagraphs": [
    "The Disco Inferno from SHARPEYE Surfboards delivers the world's fastest surfboard with Electric Performance in everyday conditions.",
    "The forerunner of the Inferno 72, the Disco Inferno is a performance shortboard that features a medium entry rocker that seamlessly flows into a flattened exit combined with a reliable, controlled medium rail. The bottom contour features a medium single concave that flows into a deep double between the fins, eventually blending into a flat exit through the tail that provides an instant burst of speed from take-off and delivers maximum speed generation whilst maintaining manoeuvrability and drive.",
